---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Y22 Recruitment"
  showPicture={true}
  background={"recruitment/banner.png"}
>
  <div class="container">
    <div>
      <div class="form-desc">
        The below link is for the form for submitting the recruitment test
        responses.
      </div>
      <div class="form-link">
        <a
          href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSebyriZQihv5TNGpvkLIuSktkIa6XsUYsb9ChWUQZEVemkWrg/viewform?"
          >Form</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text">
      <p>
        We at Team Aerial Robotics are recruiting!!! The recruitment procedure
        is straightforward. You must take a test that will be administered by
        us. Here is the test preparation material we have prepared for you:
        <a
          href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PDuuF63lxgr_c5gzbb6qjJTVrtlGNuG-/view"
        ></a>
        You are not required to completely understand all of the material's specifics.
        However, we would like you to read it and try to gain a general understanding
        and concept. We do not expect you to have any prior knowledge, and the above
        material will suffice to pass the exam. If you pass the examination, we will
        simply chat with you to learn more about you. And that's it! Check out the
        recruitment presentation and the Intro video to learn more about what we
        do and what we have achieved over the years.

        <script async src="//www.instagram.com/embed.js"></script>
        <div
          style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 0; padding-top: 56.2500%;
padding-bottom: 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(63,69,81,0.16); margin-top: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.9em; overflow: hidden;
border-radius: 8px; will-change: transform;"
        >
          <iframe
            loading="lazy"
            style="position: absolute; width: 100%; height: 100%; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0;margin: 0;"
            src="https://www.canva.com/design/DAFdDLYKQD4/view?embed"
            allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"
            allow="fullscreen"
          >
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://www.canva.com/design/DAFdDLYKQD4/view?utm_content=DAFdDLYKQD4&utm_campaign=designshare&utm_medium=embeds&utm_source=link"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"></a>
      </p>
      <div class="form-desc">Reference Material List</div>
      <div class="window">
        <iframe
          id="material-frame"
          loading="lazy"
          src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PDuuF63lxgr_c5gzbb6qjJTVrtlGNuG-/preview"
          style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 60vh; top: 0; left: 0; border: none; padding: 0;margin: 0;"
          allow="autoplay"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  .form-desc {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: larger;
    padding-left: 10vw;
    padding-right: 10vw;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .form-link {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: larger;
    margin-left: 12rem;
    margin-right: 12rem;
    border: 1px solid black;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  .form-link:hover {
    background-color: #f1f1f1;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .text {
    text-align: justify;
  }
  .sidebar {
    position: relative;
  }
  .window {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    position: relative;
    flex-direction: row;
    flex-grow: 1;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
</style>
